docs NumToText
    Converts a real number to a human-readable text label.

    docs num
        The number to format.
    done
done

func NumToText
    take num as real
    emit result as text
    fail error as text
body
    label = "Number: #{to.text(num)}"
    emit label
done

test NumToText
    r = NumToText(3.14)
    must r == "Number: 3.14"
done
